import React, {useState} from "react" import profilepic from './assets/images/profilepic.jpeg'; import { FaEnvelope } from "react-icons/fa"; import { FaMapMarkerAlt } from "react-icons/fa"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; // custom color values let hover = "rgb(179,29,38)" let normal = "rgb(197,31,41)" // testing JSON data on profile cards, in future it'll be replaced with the data from the database const facultyData = [ { profile: "profilepic", name: "Indira Bidari", designation: "Assistant Professor", department: "Computer Science And Engineering", email: "indirabidari@kletech.ac.in" }, { profile: "profilepic", name: "Uday Kulkarni", designation: "Assistant Professor", department: "Computer Science And Engineering", email: "udaykulkarni@kletech.ac.in", }, { profile: "profilepic", name: "Sneha Varur", designation: "Assistant Professor", department: "Computer Science And Engineering", email: "snehavarur@kletech.ac.in", }, { profile: "profilepic", name: "Karibassappa KG", designation: "Professor", department: "Computer Science And Engineering", email: "karibassappakg@kletech.ac.in", }, { profile: "profilepic", name: "Someshekar patil", designation: "Assistant Professor", department: "Computer Science And Engineering", email: "someshekarpatil@kletech.ac.in", }, ] // function to generate faculty profile cards function generateProfileCard() { return
{facultyData.map(data => (
{data.name}

{data.designation}

{data.department}

{data.email}
Read more
))}
} // main home function which displays the different faculties usinhg profile cards function Home() { const [selects, setSelects] = useState(); return

{selectsf}

{/* Profile cards */} {generateProfileCard()}
} export default Home;
